 API Change
 ----------

 Add "offset" to all parsing, searching, spanning functions.
   ustr_srch_fwd(s1, s2); => 1. ustr_srch_fwd(s1, 0, s2);
                             2. ustr_srch_fwd(s1, ustr_srch_fwd(s1, 0, s2), s2);
     also: ustr_srch_fwd(s1, ustr_spn_fwd(s1, 0, s2), s3);
   ustr_spn_fwd(s1, s2); => 1. ustr_spn_fwd(s1, 0, s2);
                            2. ustr_spn_fwd(s1, ustr_spn_fwd(s1, 0, s2), s2);
     also: ustr_spn_fwd(s1, ustr_srch_fwd(s1, 0, s2), s3);
   ustr_spn_fwd(s1, ustr_len(s1), s2) == BAD

   Also implies adding "len" return value to parse_uint etc.

   Don't change any of the others, just the read-only functions ... 
    most notably ustr_cmp*() doesn't change.


 TST
 ---
